                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Et vous écouterez bientôt sous le feuillage",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Les rires éclatants qui montent du village.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Vous vivez ! avril passe, et voici maintenant",
